l as forklift operator checklists, for operations to maintain maximum safety and productivity.","link":null},"annotations":{"bold":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false,"code":false,"color":"default"},"plain_text":"To celebrate National Forklift Safety Day, we’ve compiled some top forklift tire safety tips, as well as forklift operator checklists, for operations to maintain maximum safety and productivity.","href":null}],"icon":null,"color":"default"},"archived":false},{"object":"block","id":"35534d6d-7cea-8183-9af0-dd659781a439","parent":{"type":"page_id","page_id":"35534d6d-7cea-81de-9513-e203e9f3c1fc"},"created_time":"2026-05-03T22:01:00.000Z","last_edited_time":"2026-05-03T22:01:00.000Z","created_by":{"object":"user","id":"35534d6d-7cea-8179-8809-002768bc44c3"},"last_edited_by":{"object":"user","id":"35534d6d-7cea-8179-8809-002768bc44c3"},"has_children":false,"in_trash":false,"type":"paragraph","paragraph":{"rich_text":[{"type":"text","text":{"content":"Since forklift tires play a major role in ensuring operator’s safety & maximizing productivity, it’s important to know signs when it’s time to change tires, as well as how to prolong your tire life.","link":null},"annotations":{"bold":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false,"code":false,"color":"default"},"plain_text":"Since forklift tires play a major role in ensuring operator’s safety & maximizing productivity, it’s important to know signs when it’s time to change tires, as well as how to prolong your tire life.","href":null}],"icon":null,"color":"default"},"archived":false},{"object":"block","id":"35534d6d-7cea-815e-81e4-ea04d6d331b4","parent":{"type":"page_id","page_id":"35534d6d-7cea-81de-9513-e203e9f3c1fc"},"created_time":"2026-05-03T22:01:00.000Z","last_edited_time":"2026-05-03T22:01:00.000Z","created_by":{"object":"user","id":"35534d6d-7cea-8179-8809-002768bc44c3"},"last_edited_by":{"object":"user","id":"35534d6d-7cea-8179-8809-002768bc44c3"},"has_children":false,"in_trash":false,"type":"paragraph","paragraph":{"rich_text":[{"type":"text","text":{"content":"Other than checking on tire wear, there’re also signs that indicate damage on forklift tires for replacement.","link":null},"annotations":{"bold":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false,"code":false,"color":"default"},"plain_text":"Other than checking on tire wear, there’re also signs that indicate damage on forklift tires for replacement.","href":null}],"icon":null,"color":"default"},"archived":false},{"object":"block","id":"35534d6d-7cea-81b7-8f21-c12e1ab95f72","parent":{"type":"page_id","page_id":"35534d6d-7cea-81de-9513-e203e9f3c1fc"},"created_time":"2026-05-03T22:01:00.000Z","last_edited_time":"2026-05-03T22:01:00.000Z","created_by":{"object":"user","id":"35534d6d-7cea-8179-8809-002768bc44c3"},"last_edited_by":{"object":"user","id":"35534d6d-7cea-8179-8809-002768bc44c3"},"has_children":false,"in_trash":false,"type":"heading_3","heading_3":{"rich_text":[{"type":"text","text":{"content":"Press-on tires","link":null},"annotations":{"bold":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false,"code":false,"color":"default"},"plain_text":"Press-on tires","href":null}],"is_toggleable":false,"color":"default"},"archived":false},{"object":"block","id":"35534d6d-7cea-817b-a0e2-c2d9b16e30f1","parent":{"type":"page_id","page_id":"35534d6d-7cea-81de-9513-e203e9f3c1fc"},"created_time":"2026-05-03T22:01:00.000Z","last_edited_time":"2026-05-03T22:01:00.000Z","created_by":{"object":"user","id":"35534d6d-7cea-8179-8809-002768bc44c3"},"last_edited_by":{"object":"user","id":"35534d6d-7cea-8179-8809-002768bc44c3"},"has_children":false,"in_trash":false,"type":"paragraph","paragraph":{"rich_text":[{"type":"text","text":{"content":"A general rule is to identify tire wear by measuring its current width (across the tire, not up and down). If the current width is more than two inches lower than the original width, which can be found on the sidewall of the tire, then it’s time to replace the tire.","link":null},"annotations":{"bold":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false,"code":false,"color":"default"},"plain_text":"A general rule is to identify tire wear by measuring its current width (across the tire, not up and down). If the current width is more than two inches lower than the original width, which can be found on the sidewall of the tire, then it’s time to replace the tire.","href":null}],"icon":null,"color":"default"},"archived":false},{"object":"block","id":"35534d6d-7cea-814f-8cde-dcacfbe35d80","parent":{"type":"page_id","page_id":"35534d6d-7cea-81de-9513-e203e9f3c1fc"},"created_time":"2026-05-03T22:01:00.000Z","last_edited_time":"2026-05-03T22:01:00.000Z","created_by":{"object":"user","id":"35534d6d-7cea-8179-8809-002768bc44c3"},"last_edited_by":{"object":"user","id":"35534d6d-7cea-8179-8809-002768bc44c3"},"has_children":false,"in_trash":false,"type":"paragraph","paragraph":{"rich_text":[{"type":"text","text":{"content":"Another method to identify press-on tires for replacement is looking at the lettering. If the tire is worn to the top of the lettering, consider a replacement.","link":null},"annotations":{"bold":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false,"code":false,"color":"default"},"plain_text":"Another method to identify press-on tires for replacement is looking at the lettering. If the tire is worn to the top of the lettering, consider a replacement.","href":null}],"icon":null,"color":"default"},"archived":false},{"object":"block","id":"35534d6d-7cea-81df-9bc5-c65daa602c40","parent":{"type":"page_id","page_id":"35534d6d-7cea-81de-9513-e203e9f3c1fc"},"created_time":"2026-05-03T22:01:00.000Z","last_edited_time":"2026-05-03T22:01:00.000Z","created_by":{"object":"user","id":"35534d6d-7cea-8179-8809-002768bc44c3"},"last_edited_by":{"object":"user","id":"35534d6d-7cea-8179-8809-002768bc44c3"},"has_children":false,"in_trash":false,"type":"heading_3","heading_3":{"rich_text":[{"type":"text","text":{"content":"Standard pneumatic tires","link":null},"annotations":{"bold":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false,"code":false,"color":"default"},"plain_text":"Standard pneumatic tires","href":null}],"is_toggleable":false,"color":"default"},"archived":false},{"object":"block","id":"35534d6d-7cea-81ed-b9d5-de9cb484bcf0","parent":{"type":"page_id","page_id":"35534d6d-7cea-81de-9513-e203e9f3c1fc"},"created_time":"2026-05-03T22:01:00.000Z","last_edited_time":"2026-05-03T22:01:00.000Z","created_by":{"object":"user","id":"35534d6d-7cea-8179-8809-002768bc44c3"},"last_edited_by":{"object":"user","id":"35534d6d-7cea-8179-8809-002768bc44c3"},"has_children":false,"in_trash":false,"type":"paragraph","paragraph":{"rich_text":[{"type":"text","text":{"content":"For standard pneumatic forklift tires, once the tire’s tread has worn to the point where it’s becoming invisible or you can see bald spots on the tire, consider a replacement.","link":null},"annotations":{"bold":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false,"code":false,"color":"default"},"plain_text":"For standard pneumatic forklift tires, once the tire’s tread has worn to the point where it’s becoming invisible or you can see bald spots on the tire, consider a replacement.","href":null}],"icon":null,"color":"default"},"archived":false},{"object":"block","id":"35534d6d-7cea-8151-9f7c-e0466d74c63c","parent":{"type":"page_id","page_id":"35534d6d-7cea-81de-9513-e203e9f3c1fc"},"created_time":"2026-05-03T22:01:00.000Z","last_edited_time":"2026-05-03T22:01:00.000Z","created_by":{"object":"user","id":"35534d6d-7cea-8179-8809-002768bc44c3"},"last_edited_by":{"object":"user","id":"35534d6d-7cea-8179-8809-002768bc44c3"},"has_children":false,"in_trash":false,"type":"heading_3","heading_3":{"rich_text":[{"type":"text","text":{"content":"Solid pneumatic / resilient tires","link":null},"annotations":{"bold":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false,"code":false,"color":"default"},"plain_text":"Solid pneumatic / resilient tires","href":null}],"is_toggleable":false,"color":"default"},"archived":false},{"object":"block","id":"35534d6d-7cea-8135-9a4b-d28fc543e5f3","parent":{"type":"page_id","page_id":"35534d6d-7cea-81de-9513-e203e9f3c1fc"},"created_time":"2026-05-03T22:01:00.000Z","last_edited_time":"2026-05-03T22:01:00.000Z","created_by":{"object":"user","id":"35534d6d-7cea-8179-8809-002768bc44c3"},"last_edited_by":{"object":"user","id":"35534d6d-7cea-8179-8809-002768bc44c3"},"has_children":false,"in_trash":false,"type":"paragraph","paragraph":{"rich_text":[{"type":"text","text":{"content":"For solid pneumatic tires, inspect the wear band and if it’s exposed, it’s time to replace your resilient forklift tires. Here is a list of signs that identify damaged forklift tires and what to do about them.","link":null},"annotations":{"bold":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false,"code":false,"color":"default"},"plain_text":"For solid pneumatic tires, inspect the wear band and if it’s exposed, it’s time to replace your resilient forklift tires. Here is a list of signs that identify damaged forklift tires and what to do about them.","href":null}],"icon":null,"color":"default"},"archived":false},{"object":"block","id":"35534d6d-7cea-819a-b540-f019dd3e3c49","parent":{"type":"page_id","page_id":"35534d6d-7cea-81de-9513-e203e9f3c1fc"},"created_time":"2026-05-03T22:01:00.000Z","last_edited_time":"2026-05-03T22:01:00.000Z","created_by":{"object":"user","id":"35534d6d-7cea-8179-8809-002768bc44c3"},"last_edited_by":{"object":"user","id":"35534d6d-7cea-8179-8809-002768bc44c3"},"has_children":false,"in_trash":false,"type":"paragraph","paragraph":{"rich_text":[{"type":"text","text":{"content":"In general, here are four common sign to determine when to replace your tire:","link":null},"annotations":{"bold":true,"italic":true,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false,"code":false,"color":"default"},"plain_text":"In general, here are four common sign to determine when to replace your tire:","href":null}],"icon":null,"color":"default"},"archived":false},{"object":"block","id":"35534d6d-7cea-81f4-b02e-f668af55131d","parent":{"type":"page_id","page_id":"35534d6d-7cea-81de-9513-e203e9f3c1fc"},"created_time":"2026-05-03T22:01:00.000Z","last_edited_time":"2026-05-03T22:01:00.000Z","created_by":{"object":"user","id":"35534d6d-7cea-8179-8809-002768bc44c3"},"last_edited_by":{"object":"user","id":"35534d6d-7cea-8179-8809-002768bc44c3"},"has_children":false,"in_trash":false,"type":"bulleted_list_item","bulleted_list_item":{"rich_text":[{"type":"text","text":{"content":"Tire wear and balding","link":null},"annotations":{"bold":false,"italic":true,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false,"code":false,"color":"default"},"plain_text":"Tire wear and balding","href":null}],"color":"default"},"archived":false},{"object":"block","id":"35534d6d-7cea-8117-bbc8-c3107ee7a405","parent":{"type":"page_id","page_id":"35534d6d-7cea-81de-9513-e203e9f3c1fc"},"created_time":"2026-05-03T22:01:00.000Z","last_edited_time":"2026-05-03T22:01:00.000Z","created_by":{"object":"user","id":"35534d6d-7cea-8179-8809-002768bc44c3"},"last_edited_by":{"object":"user","id":"35534d6d-7cea-8179-8809-002768bc44c3"},"has_children":false,"in_trash":false,"type":"paragraph","paragraph":{"rich_text":[{"type":"text","text":{"content":"Both pneumatic and solid tires will become less effective as their tread wears down. For pneumatic tires, if the tread is nearly gone or you notice bald spots, it’s time to replace the tires. For solid cushion tires, when the size of the tire is more than 2 in. less than their original size, it’s time for new tires.","link":null},"annotations":{"bold":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false,"code":false,"color":"default"},"plain_text":"Both pneumatic and solid tires will become less effective as their tread wears down. For pneumatic tires, if the tread is nearly gone or you notice bald spots, it’s time to replace the tires. For solid cushion tires, when the size of the tire is more than 2 in. less than their original size, it’s time for new tires.","href":null}],"icon":null,"color":"default"},"archived":false},{"object":"block","id":"35534d6d-7cea-81b1-a16b-c4d145815bb4","parent":{"type":"page_id","page_id":"35534d6d-7cea-81de-9513-e203e9f3c1fc"},"created_time":"2026-05-03T22:01:00.000Z","last_edited_time":"2026-05-03T22:01:00.000Z","created_by":{"object":"user","id":"35534d6d-7cea-8179-8809-002768bc44c3"},"last_edited_by":{"object":"user","id":"35534d6d-7cea-8179-8809-002768bc44c3"},"has_children":false,"in_trash":false,"type":"bulleted_list_item","bulleted_list_item":{"rich_text":[{"type":"text","text":{"content":"Tire chunking","link":null},"annotations":{"bold":false,"italic":true,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false,"code":false,"color":"default"},"plain_text":"Tire chunking","href":null}],"color":"default"},"archived":false},{"object":"block","id":"35534d6d-7cea-81f8-9fb1-de2725234d10","parent":{"type":"page_id","page_id":"35534d6d-7cea-81de-9513-e203e9f3c1fc"},"created_time":"2026-05-03T22:01:00.000Z","last_edited_time":"2026-05-03T22:01:00.000Z","created_by":{"object":"user","id":"35534d6d-7cea-8179-8809-002768bc44c3"},"last_edited_by":{"object":"user","id":"35534d6d-7cea-8179-8809-002768bc44c3"},"has_children":false,"in_trash":false,"type":"paragraph","paragraph":{"rich_text":[{"type":"text","text":{"content":"If pieces, or chunks, of your forklift tires are falling off, that’s a good sign you need to replace them.","link":null},"annotations":{"bold":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false,"code":false,"color":"default"},"plain_text":"If pieces, or chunks, of your forklift tires are falling off, that’s a good sign you need to replace them.","href":null}],"icon":null,"color":"default"},"archived":false},{"object":"block","id":"35534d6d-7cea-8170-8a99-eea957090162","parent":{"type":"page_id","page_id":"35534d6d-7cea-81de-9513-e